In re Resignation of Hartwell.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Hartwell (1996), 75 Ohio St.3d 1202.]

(No. 96-400 Submitted and decided March 6, 1996.)

The resignation as an attorney of Leda Cossack Hartwell, a.k.a. Leda M. Hartwell, of Westerville, Ohio, Attorney Registration No. 0020828, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer and Cook, JJ., concur.
